Donation Requests



Please download our Donation Request Application here.
Submit a copy of your IRS letter confirming your nonprofit status and the completed application by email only to: lelia@chjwealthmanagement.com.
All requests must be received at least 6 WEEKS prior to the date your donation is needed.
Please note:  A completed application does not guarantee a donation.
Incomplete applications and insufficient lead times will not be considered.
You will be contacted by our Brand Ambassador if your donation request is fulfilled.
Thank you for giving us the opportunity to review your request.

 


























 
