Lelia Lee


Brand Ambassador




Lelia is an accomplished executive with over 30 years’ experience in the fashion and food industries in New York.  As Vice President of both industries with P&L responsibilities, she managed all aspects of marketing, design, product development and international sourcing.
She now oversees all charitable giving opportunities, community partnerships and marketing for the organization ensuring the company’s high standards of excellence are reflected in all branding endeavors.
