 Welcome








Carlton, Hofferkamp and Jenks Wealth Management, LLC is an independent, fee-only registered investment advisory firm located in The Woodlands, Texas.












 


Ranked among Top Houston Area Wealth Management Firms and Practices by Houston Business Journal.


 












Recipients of prestigious Five Star Wealth Manager award for six consecutive years.







 











 Welcome








Carlton, Hofferkamp and Jenks Wealth Management, LLC is an independent, fee-only registered investment advisory firm located in The Woodlands, Texas.












 


Ranked among Top Houston Area Wealth Management Firms and Practices by Houston Business Journal.


 












Recipients of prestigious Five Star Wealth Manager award for six consecutive years.







 





Why Experience Matters


Our team’s talent has been tested through many business cycles 
and periods of market volatility such as:




Black Monday Crash of 1987
|
Asian Crisis in 1997
|
DotCom Crash in 2000
|
Housing Bubble and Credit Crisis in 2008-2009 (and the continuing effects)




The investment knowledge we’ve gained through these experiences along with our time-tested philosophy, diligent money management and consistent communication in all market environments enable us to guide and protect our clients through these critical times.




“The only source of knowledge is experience” – Albert Einstein 

